        <item>
            <title>神改便攜式 Mac Mini   桌面機化身隨身工作站</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/portable-mac-mini/3d-%e6%89%93%e5%8d%b0/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=portable-mac-mini</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/portable-mac-mini/3d-%e6%89%93%e5%8d%b0/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 28 Apr 2025 08:50:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[3D 打印]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305258</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在行動辦公成為新常態的今天，桌面電腦是否還只能困守一隅？近日有一位 YouTuber 自己動手，成功將 Apple 最新 M4 Mac Mini 創造成一款可攜式裝置，結合鍵盤、觸控螢幕及創新的 3D 列印結構，不但大幅提升機動性，還保留了原有性能與擴充性，為愛好 DIY 與行動工作者帶來全新啟發。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>重新定義 Mac Mini 使用方式</h2><p>影片創作者表示，收到不少觀眾留言，期待看到新的 Mac Mini 改裝作品。當他實際上手 Mac Mini，發現其極致小巧的機身後，便萌生了「讓桌機隨身攜帶」的想法。有別於以往需要額外攜帶鍵盤的設計，這次他選擇將 Apple 的 Magic Keyboard 直接融入結構中，再搭配一塊支援 VESA 標準的觸控螢幕，大小幾乎與鍵盤一致。這塊螢幕只需一條連接線即可驅動，兼具便攜與功能性，成為可攜式 Mac Mini 的關鍵組件。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>巧妙設計，解決平衡與收納問題</h2><p>由於螢幕重量明顯大於鍵盤，為防止翻倒，創作者靈機一動，利用 Mac Mini 本體為鍵盤側邊增重，巧妙解決結構平衡問題。同時為避免遮擋插槽與電源鍵，他將 Mac Mini 橫向置於螢幕下方，既維持美觀，也符合人體工學。所有核心零件，包括螢幕連接線、散熱孔、風扇進氣口及各式插槽，都在設計中被完整保留，不影響日常使用。而 Mac Mini 本體則透過魔術膠帶固定，方便拆卸與維護。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
